				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Magnesium hydroxide is a natural mineral that reduces stomach acid and increases water in the intestines. It is used as a laxative to relieve constipation, and as an antacid to relieve indigestion, sour stomach, and heartburn. It is a white solid with low solubility in water and a common component of antacids. It is a common element in seawater and can be extracted from seawater by alkalinisation or lime. It is used in the pharmaceutical industry as a tablet and capsule diluent.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">氢氧化镁是一种天然矿物质，能减少胃酸，增加肠道中的水分。它可作为泻药缓解便秘，也可作为抗酸剂缓解消化不良、胃酸和胃灼热。它是一种白色固体，在水中的溶解度很低，是抗酸剂的常见成分。它是海水中的一种常见元素，可通过碱化或石灰从海水中提取。它在制药业中用作片剂和胶囊稀释剂。</common:generalComment>
